      <title>德意志银行称区块链可以帮助缓解利润压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/deutsche-bank-says-blockchains-can-help-weather-margin-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行表示，数字资产领域的区块链技术为银行应对金融服务利润率压缩提供了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/deutsche-bank-says-blockchains-can-help-weather-margin-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
